immigrate

Create a public var in this namespace for each public var in the namespaces named by ns-names. The created vars have the same name, value and metadata as the original except that their :ns metadata value is this namespace.

File: overtone/helpers/ns.clj Line: 3 

      (defn immigrate
 "Create a public var in this namespace for each public var in the
 namespaces named by ns-names. The created vars have the same name, value
 and metadata as the original except that their :ns metadata value is this
 namespace."
 [& ns-names]
 (doseq [ns ns-names]
   (doseq [[sym var] (ns-publics ns)]
     (let [sym (with-meta sym (assoc (meta var) :orig-ns ns))]
       (if (.isBound var)
         (intern *ns* sym (if (fn? (var-get var))
                            var
                            (var-get var)))
         (intern *ns* sym))))))
